                <h2 class="main_head">Your trusted machinery partner for all PP/PE needs</h2>
                <p> At Armstrong, we combine innovation, quality, and precision at every step. From deep research, sourcing top-quality materials, and designing products to rigorous testing and following international standards, we use advanced technology to deliver finishing machines that are reliable, efficient, and built to perform. </p>
                <p>Our in-house production facility manufactures a wide range of machinery and spare parts for customers worldwide. This includes fabric-cutting machines, PP woven bag lamination machines, belt cutting and sewing machines, bag cleaning machines, and liner sealing machines. Whether you need a single machine, a complete PP woven bag plant, or just a spare part, we’ve got you covered!</p>

